<p>Thanks JVC for corrections of <hi rend="italic">Movement in plants</hi>. Sends a clarifying sentence.</p>  
<p><hi rend="italic">Earthworms</hi> nearly done – "a small book of little moment".</p> 
            <p>Reports his health is better than it was, "but I have little strength &amp; feel very old".</p>
